assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: ISOTeam Ltd. operates in the building maintenance and estate upgrading industry in Singapore. The company operates through Repair and Redecoration; Addition and Alteration; Coatings and Paintings; and Others segments. It offers waterproofing and reroofing, improvement works, routine property maintenance, and team contract works, as well as repainting, repair, and redecoration services; neighborhood renewal, hawker centers upgrading, estate upgrading, home improvement, and electrical load upgrading services; and new build painting, eco-friendly coating, architectural and protecting coating, and fireproofing and niche industrial coating services. The company also provides electrical and mechanical ventilation works, air conditioning work, sanitary and plumbing, and solar panel installation services; commercial A&A and engineering works, building, architectural and commercial interior construction solutions, and advanced building technologies; and interior design and fitting out, designing and building, home retrofit and fit-out, and property maintenance and enhancement services. In addition, it offers vertical greening, horticultural services and maintenance, floating wetlands systems, niche landscaping, and gardening and landscaping maintenance services; thermal insulating plasters, anti-slip floor coatings, green label intumescent fire proofing coatings, composite timber decking, renewable energy installation, and cockroaches and odor remover services; and access equipment services, including leasing of boom lifts, scissor lifts, personal lift, forklifts, and telehandlers. Further, the company provides handyman services, such as home care and upgrading, and general repairs and maintenance services; bike sharing services; home painting services; and pest control services; and consultancy, project management, building program advisory, vector control, and electrical engineering services. ISOTeam Ltd. was founded in 1998 and is based in Singapore.
